title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 10 - new build available
description:
In this video we will review what has changed in the latest build which has been released as part of the Sim Update 10 beta testing. It will bump up the version of MSFS to 1.27.14.0. Based on the release notes most fixes are to prevent crash to desktop (CTD's) and some other issues as well. In this version also to issues have been specifically resolved for the Xbox although it looks like those are graphical issues.
